PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1997-909 that will allow the CANADIAN PACIFIC RAILWAY COMPANY to amend the lease held by INTER-PRO PROPERTY CORPORATION on the South Edmonton (Strathcona) Station in EDMONTON, ALBERTA, by granting the lessee the option to twice renew the lease, for a term of five years each time, for a total tenure of twenty (20) years.
